ased our latest update, WPtouch 1.9.42, which includes a slew of new enhancements to help make your WPtouch powered site even better!</p>\n<h3>New in design features</h3>\n<p>We&#8217;ve more than doubled your options for background choices by adding 8 new backgrounds as well as an updated default background. New additions include: Crossed Stripes, Fiber, Light Noise, Low Contrast Linen, Random Grey, Stitched Wool, White Carbon and White Carbon Fiber.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve also added some sleek new Twitter and Facebook share logos.</p>\n<h3>Better usability</h3>\n<p>Our latest version of WPtouch features an updated search tool with improved usability, a new &#8216;Menu&#8217; text button and an updated CSS only mobile switch.</p>\n<p>A full list of changes included in the new release can be found below. Update now to try out these new enhancements for yourself!</p>\n<h3>Changelog</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: 8 new background options, updated default background</li>\n<li>Updated: Twitter and Facebook share logos</li>\n<li>Updated: Changed drop menu arrow to text button</li>\n<li>Updated: Enhanced usability of search</li>\n<li>Updated: Changed mobile switch link to CSS only</li>\n<li>Updated: Prefixes for Opera, Mozilla browsers</li>\n<li>Updated: General styling updates</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2012/07/new-update-wptouch-1-9-42-now-available/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"10\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		