astle Partnership in 2007 and spent two years working as a  trainee solicitor and Police Station Representative before qualifying as a solicitor in September 2009. Tim specialises in criminal defence work.\r\n\r\nTim’s  training has given him extensive experience in dealing with a wide cross section of offences at the Police Station and Crown Court.  In addition to his Police Station and Crown Court work he now, as a qualified solicitor, appears in the  Magistrates Court on a regular basis.\r\n\r\nTim’s application for Duty Solicitor status is pending  and he plans to apply for advocacy rights in the Crown Court in the near future.\r\n\r\nHe has a particular interest in offences relating to the supply of controlled substances.\r\n[/column]\r\n[end_columns]', 'Tim Cosham', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tim', '', '', '2010-04-07 10:44:21', '2010-04-07 10:44:21', '', '2', 'http://castle.creativitea.co.uk/?page_id=185', '0', 'page', '', '0'), ('186', '1', '2010-02-11 16:35:51', '2010-02-11 16:35:51', '', 'blankperson_profile', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'blankperson_profile', '', '', '2010-02-11 16:35:51', '2010-02-11 16:35:51', '', '185', 'http://castle.creativitea.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/blankperson_profile.jpg', '0', 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', '0'), ('187', '1', '2010-02-11 16:35:28', '2010-02-11 16:35:28', '', 'Tim', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '185-revision', '', '', '2010-02-11 16:35:28', '2010-02-11 16:35:28', '', '185', 'http://castle.creativitea.co.uk/2010/02/185-revision/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('188', '1', '2010-02-11 16:04:20', '2010-02-11 16:04:20', 'John qualified as a solicitor in 1987.  He has specialised in criminal defence for over 20 years and has been a Duty Solicitor for the Police Station and Magistrates Court during that time.\r\nJohn is a qualified Solicitor Advocate in the Crown Court which enables him to appear at the Crown Court.\r\nIn addition to his criminal workload , he also manages the Guildford of