tachment_178\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"230\" caption=\"John Evans - Partner\"]<a href=\"/about-us/john-evans/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-178\" title=\"John Evans\" src=\"/images/john_evans_wide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"150\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_178\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"230\" caption=\"Ian Wilkinson - Partner\"]<a href=\"/about-us/ian-wilkinson/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-178\" title=\"Ian Wilkinson\" src=\"/images/ian_wilkinson_wide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"150\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_178\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"230\" caption=\"Sinéad Willox (née McNally) - Partner\"]<a href=\"/about-us/sinead-willox/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-178\" title=\"Sinéad Willox (neé McNally)\" src=\"/images/sinead_willox_wide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"150\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_178\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"230\" caption=\"Tim Cosham\"]<a href=\"/about-us/tim/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-178\" title=\"Tim Cosham\" src=\"/images/tim_cosham_wide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"150\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_178\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"230\" caption=\"Kate Holbrook\"]<a href=\"/about-us/kate/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-178\" title=\"Kate Holbrook\" src=\"/images/kate_holbrook_wide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"150\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_178\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"230\" caption=\"Kate Quincey\"]<a href=\"/about-us/katie/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-178\" title=\"Katie Quincey\" src=\"/images/katie_quincey_wide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"150\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_178\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"230\" caption=\"Eleanor Towsey\"]<a href=\"/about-us/eleanor/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-178\" title=\"Eleanor Towsey\" src=\"/images/eleanor_towsey_wide.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"150\" /></a>[/caption]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-52', '', '', '2011-09-19 14:18:04', '2011-09-19 14:18:04', '', '2', 'http://www.castlepartnership.co.uk/2011/09/2-revision-52/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('346', '1', '2011-09-19 14:14:01', '2011-09-19 14:14:01', '[column width=\"30%\" padding=\"3%\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-186 alignleft\" title=\"blankperson_profile\" src=\"/images/eleanor_towsey_main.jpg\" alt=\"Eleanor Towsey\" width=\"210\" height=\"210\" />[/column]\r\n[column width=\"57%\" padding=\"0\"]Eleanor Towsey graduated from the University of London with a degree in French and Spanish  in 2002 and an MA in French and European Critical Theory in 2003. Eleanor has had a successful first career in Hospitality Management and, early on in her career, was promoted to General Manager of several high profile  restaurants based in Birmingham and in London.\r\n\r\nBetween 2008 and 2010 she went on to complete the Graduate Diploma in Law and the Legal Practice Course at the College of Law in Guildford. Eleanor had spent the last year working in a commercial firm as a fee-earner  in contract, travel and personal injury law. She joined the Castle Partnership in August 2011 as a trainee solicitor.\r\n\r\nEleanor qualified as a Police Station Accredited Representative in July 2011. She is currently assisting Sinead Willox  in running the Hampshire office, based in Basingstoke.\r\n[/column]\r\n[end_columns]', 'Eleanor Towsey', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '339-revision-3', '', '', '2011-09-19 14:14:01', '2011-09-19 14:14:01', '', '339', 'http://www.castlepartnership.co.uk/2011/09/339-revision-3/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('347', '1', '2011-10-06 14:10:53', '2011-10-06 14:10:53', '[column width=\"30%\" padding=\"3%\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-186 alignleft\" title=\"blankperson_profile\" src=\"/images/eleanor_towsey_main.jpg\" alt=\"Eleanor Towsey\" width=\"210\" height=\"210\" />[/column]\r\n[column width=\"57%\" 